   "source": [
    "profile_dimensions = csv(\"\"\"\n",
    "nr,name,r\n",
    "P0,0,30\n",
    "P1,1,35\n",
    "P2,2,40\n",
    "P3,3,45\n",
    "P4,4,50\n",
    "P5,5,55\n",
    "P6,6,60\n",
    "P7,6a,65\n",
    "\"\"\")\n",
    "unit = 'cm'\n",
    "profile_dimensions"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 15,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "______________________________\n",
      "Pr_P0  ->  0\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "no = 'P0'\n",
    "name, r = profile_dimensions.loc[no].values\n",
    "R = 3 * r\n",
    "roh = r / 2\n",
    "height = r * 3\n",
    "width = r * 2\n",
    "# h1 = roh - (r + roh) / (R - roh) * roh\n",
    "h1 = r/ 5\n",
    "\n",
    "cross_section = CrossSection(label=no, long_label=name, width=width, height=height, unit=unit)\n",
    "cross_section.add(circle(roh, x_m=roh))\n",
    "cross_section.add(h1)\n",
    "cross_section.add(circle(R, x_m=2 * r, y_m=-(R - r)))\n",
    "cross_section.add(2 * r)\n",
    "cross_section.add(circle(r, x_m=2 * r))"
   ]
